title: Greenwood QB Luke Hales talks recruiting and more
text:
Greenwood QB Luke Hales talks recruiting and more Luke Matheson CLICK HERE TO SUBSCRIBE TO ARKANSASVARSITY.COM - JUST 33 CENTS PER DAY Greenwood QB Luke Hales was 9 of 13 passing for 236 yards and four touchdowns, and ran the ball seven times for 37 yards an a touchdown in a 56-19 victory over Conway on Friday night. 
Hales spoke with ArkansasVarsity.com about his performance in the game, recruiting, and more. CLICK HERE FOR THE INTERVIEW
